        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "); behold, these peoples recompense us by coming to cast us out of our possession which Thou hast given us (הורישׁ, to give as a possession, as in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Judges 11:24",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). There follows hereupon in ",
        "children": []
