        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Chronicles 20:12",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " the prayer: \"Our God, wilt Thou not judge,\" i.e., do right upon them, for we have not strength before (to withstand) this multitude? We know not what to do, sc. against so many enemies; but our eyes are turned to Thee, i.e., to Thee we look for help; cf. ",
